t=\"(bgm38)\">然而脑子和脑子还是有差别，很多东西是记不住的","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/02/68/26866.jpg","floor":"#27","id":"1322344","time":"2018-2-28 22:58","userId":"hc","userName":"月火","userSign":"(おのれ！これで勝ったと思うなよぉ!!! ...)","message":"很少专门写笔记<br>代码的笔记直接抄代码到Lab project、写comment<br>作画的笔记直接写在草稿旁边<br>只有梦醒起床、生活上想到有什么点子才写笔记<br>还有看到特别喜欢的<span style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">　　</span>女优<br><br>工作进度倒是会写笔记<br>Evernote有个tickbox，用来做to-do list非常棒<br>没这个我肯定记不住今天要做什么工作<br>连昨天写到哪段都会忘记","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/25/78/257815.jpg","floor":"#27-1","id":"1322437","time":"2018-3-1 09:34","userId":"yanshe","userName":"九八式衍射弹","userSign":"","message":"你这个黑块真的只是黑块 不能反白啊<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/18/90/189040.jpg","floor":"#28","id":"1322350","time":"2018-2-28 23:13","userId":"prevails","userName":"Donuts","userSign":"","message":"VS Code 纯文本","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/25/42/254224.jpg","floor":"#29","id":"1322353","time":"2018-2-28 23:22","userId":"ntmarie","userName":"ntmarie","userSign":"(你好啊)","message":"我纸笔手写的都","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/42/4286.jpg","floor":"#30","id":"1322354","time":"2018-2-28 23:29","userId":"iqbee","userName":"友人Bee⭐️v0.2","userSign":"(只要能点格子就好了)","message":"以前用evernote的时候强调使用tags，但是后来tags越来越庞大，同义词或者相近的词太多，而且每次都要想个keyword，后来感觉evernote变成个垃圾桶，于是砍掉重练<br>evernote二代目用来剪藏&收集<br>经过提炼和消化后会注入OneNote<br><br>但是我当时用OneNote的时候，检索的功能做得真的很烂，不得不添加一些辅助标签<br>专业知识全都是用OneNote记载，A4方便，笔记方便，而且很适合不断订正。<br><br>后来因为工作上的原因，使用了有道云（感觉多级目录代替了tag）+OneNote<br>工作和生活方面的内容完全用有道云了，虽然有道的排版超级烂、程序也烂.......<br><br>几乎每隔一段时间就会重新检视笔记，断·离·舍&整合、作目录、修内容，使得笔记有点活力，以便工作的时候极速调用。<br>大修过几次，太磨人了，后续就有空的时候检视一下。<br>（不会用笔记自带的to do list，效率太低，主要是笔记的形式不方便）","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/25/78/257815.jpg","floor":"#30-1","id":"1322438","time":"2018-3-1 09:35","userId":"yanshe","userName":"九八式衍射弹","userSign":"","message":"OneNote检索烂在哪啊 感觉挺好使的<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/42/4286.jpg","floor":"#30-2","id":"1322504","time":"2018-3-1 15:44","userId":"iqbee","userName":"友人Bee⭐️v0.2","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">九八式衍射弹</span> 说: OneNote检索烂在哪啊 感觉挺好使的</q></div>原文打出来都搜不到啊<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/25/78/257815.jpg","floor":"#30-3","id":"1322600","time":"2018-3-1 21:06","userId":"yanshe","userName":"九八式衍射弹","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">友人Bee⭐️v0.2</span> 说: 原文打出来都搜不到啊</q></div>欸 不至于吧 我搜索连墨迹里和图片里的字都搜的出来"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/42/4286.jpg","floor":"#30-4","id":"1322740","time":"2018-3-2 09:24","userId":"iqbee","userName":"友人Bee⭐️v0.2","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">九八式衍射弹</span> 说: 欸 不至于吧 我搜索连墨迹里和图片里的字都搜的出来</q></div>是以前觉得这个特牛逼<br><br>检索这个问题，以前在微软的论坛也有人反映过的，就是中文才有这个问题，英文就没有，开始以为是检索索引的问题，搞了几次还是一样。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/25/78/257815.jpg","floor":"#30-5","id":"1322752","time":"2018-3-2 10:13","userId":"yanshe","userName":"九八式衍射弹","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">友人Bee⭐️v0.2</span> 说: 是以前觉得这个特牛逼<br><br>检索这个问题，以前在微软的论坛也有人反映过的，就是中文才有这个问题，英文就没有，开始以为是检索索引的问题，搞了几次还是一样。</q></div>原来是中文的问题啊<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/77/317704.jpg","floor":"#30-6","id":"1328459","time":"2018-3-17 22:57","userId":"317704","userName":"NekoNull","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">九八式衍射弹</span> 说: 原来是中文的问题啊</q></div>搜索的时候左右加双引号部分时候可以解决问题，但是只是部分时候<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/42/4286.jpg","floor":"#30-7","id":"1328472","time":"2018-3-17 23:11","userId":"iqbee","userName":"友人Bee⭐️v0.2","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">纱夜抱着榴弹炮</span> 说: 搜索的时候左右加双引号部分时候可以解决问题，但是只是部分时候</q></div>我现在偶尔用感觉情况好很多了，不知道还会不会这样"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/43/244318.jpg","floor":"#31","id":"1322360","time":"2018-3-1 00:29","userId":"ipcjs","userName":"ipcjs","userSign":"","message":"用Evernote，添加tag，印象笔记的搜索功能不怎么行，有的时候也会在笔记结尾添加一些用于搜索的关键字。<br>比较少直接剪藏网页，一般是把看到的知识点总结一下，自己转述出来，同时在笔记中记录网页的链接，方便需要用的时候看。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/44/294437.jpg","floor":"#32","id":"1322445","time":"2018-3-1 10:21","userId":"m45","userName":"M45","userSign":"(雪是物哀审美的重要意象)","message":"不用花里胡哨的东西。只用教材和自己的课堂笔记本。<br>对我来说笔记在电脑上再写一遍是浪费时间，效率不如手写，而且再看一遍也很花时间。<br>不如熟练掌握自己的教材和笔记本，需要什么知识点知道往哪翻，比不能Ctrl+F的电子版高效多了。<br>当然复习的时候会单独默写整理一些知识结构，这是后话。","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/43/244318.jpg","floor":"#32-1","id":"1322710","time":"2018-3-2 01:52","userId":"ipcjs","userName":"ipcjs","userSign":"","message":"电子版的优点不就是能搜索吗？"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/77/317704.jpg","floor":"#32-2","id":"1328460","time":"2018-3-17 22:57","userId":"317704","userName":"NekoNull","userSign":"","message":"电子版不能Ctrl+F ?"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/05/56/55668.jpg","floor":"#33","id":"1322467","time":"2018-3-1 11:58","userId":"hezi62","userName":"Citrate","userSign":"(万年拖延症。)","message":"有道云笔记（。好像就是个山寨版Evernote？挺符合<span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">中国人</span>我自己的使用习惯的，而且免费啊<br>课件和讲义的整理就通过电脑的文件夹整理完成","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/09/67/96745.jpg","floor":"#34","id":"1322687","time":"2018-3-2 00:27","userId":"florabaldem","userName":"群青入道云","userSign":"(愛はパワーだよ)","message":"现在发现还是用word实在（。）","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/16/50/165027.jpg","floor":"#35","id":"1322694","time":"2018-3-2 00:58","userId":"chiyahoho","userName":"chiya","userSign":"","message":"markdown + git<br>该有的真的都有了，甚至比很多工具都做得好","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/19/211931.jpg","floor":"#36","id":"1322748","time":"2018-3-2 10:00","userId":"dhzy","userName":"dhzy","userSign":"","message":"很少做笔记。你们不觉得笔记的内容一写出来就抛之脑后了吗……","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/10/1010.jpg","floor":"#36-1","id":"1328229","time":"2018-3-17 11:05","userId":"fireattack","userName":"烈之斩","userSign":"","message":"不写出来还是抛之脑后（"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/19/211931.jpg","floor":"#36-2","id":"1328372","time":"2018-3-17 19:49","userId":"dhzy","userName":"dhzy","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">烈之斩</span> 说: 不写出来还是抛之脑后（</q></div>不写就会强行记住！"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/04/210454.jpg","floor":"#36-3","id":"1328906","time":"2018-3-18 22:50","userId":"mp4spig","userName":"🌸九重凛🌸","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">dhzy(id: dhzy)</span> 说: 不写就会强行记住！</q></div>好记性不如烂笔头<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/61.gif\" smileid=\"100\" alt=\"(bgm84)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/19/211931.jpg","floor":"#36-4","id":"1328961","time":"2018-3-19 00:49","userId":"dhzy","userName":"dhzy","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">九重凛</span> 说: 好记性不如烂笔头</q></div>还不如一块硬盘"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/06/64/66443.jpg","floor":"#37","id":"1328219","time":"2018-3-17 10:13","userId":"gates_ice","userName":"示申イ山","userSign":"(蛋定能生出个鸟来！)","message":"OneNote是好，但是问题就在于跨平台（支持云同步？）版的笔记和Windows版的笔记是不同的版本不互相兼容的！","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/92/9278.jpg","floor":"#37-1","id":"1329034","time":"2018-3-19 10:04","userId":"butakami","userName":"Ijijyo Akiku","userSign":"","message":"是吗？为啥我在Windows上做的笔记能同步到多平台？是不是版本问题？"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/06/64/66443.jpg","floor":"#37-2","id":"1329347","time":"2018-3-20 05:13","userId":"gates_ice","userName":"示申イ山","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Girasolia</span> 说: 是吗？为啥我在Windows上做的笔记能同步到多平台？是不是版本问题？</q></div>微软能同步到全平台的OneNote是个子集。Windows桌面版的才是完全体"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/25/85/258588.jpg","floor":"#38","id":"1328288","time":"2018-3-17 14:26","userId":"258588","userName":"joegnis","userSign":"","message":"没有用 Workflowy/Dynalist 做笔记的嘛。Bullet point 的设计太好了，无限层级，收缩自如，整理知识的利器。就是界面不好看，App做的一般。需要专注写点什么的时候，我在iPad上用Day One写，最近出了 Android 版本，能在手机上写了。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/78/177820.jpg","floor":"#39","id":"1328442","time":"2018-3-17 22:41","userId":"franklinyu","userName":"Franklin Yu","userSign":"(讓一切都自動化！)","message":"先谷歌搜一下，能在第一頁出現的就不記了……<br><br>然後去 Stack Exchange 搜一下，搜不到的就<a href=\"https://stackoverflow.blog/2011/07/01/its-ok-to-ask-and-answer-your-own-questions/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">自問自答</a>","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/06/04/60431.jpg","floor":"#40","id":"1328452","time":"2018-3-17 22:48","userId":"auppyanthony","userName":"otaku","userSign":"(是贪婪的人 渴望被爱 被拥抱 被理解 被接受 又是自私 ...)","message":"思维导图？<br><br>不过我还是觉得记在真正的笔记本里的好，记在电脑里的大部分都变成硬盘垃圾了。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/77/317704.jpg","floor":"#41","id":"1328464","time":"2018-3-17 23:02","userId":"317704","userName":"NekoNull","userSign":"","message":"Onenote 作为正经笔记本，记录需要长久储存的东西（e.g. 课堂笔记），设好了 Ctrl + 1/2/3... 加各种格式，考前/周末回顾很方便（事实上不会的...）<br>CintaNotes 作为临时笔记本，见到什么想存下来的直接 Ctrl + Shift + C 就可以存入笔记本（快捷键经过修改），再根据自己设置的各种规则自动加 tag，感觉还是挺爽的...<br>然而有的科目，比如高数，在没有 Surface 及类似设备的情况下，还是乖乖手写吧，不然光是公式就会烦死人...<br>有的时候整理框架，还是会选择手写或者用幕布 / Workflowy 等层级笔记工具<br>然而 Onenote 的中文字体和搜索问题到现在都没解决，不知道巨硬怎么想的","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/04/210454.jpg","floor":"#41-1","id":"1328905","time":"2018-3-18 22:49","userId":"mp4spig","userName":"🌸九重凛🌸","userSign":"","message":"虽然我没用过Office 365，不过听说365解决得挺好"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/56/295606.jpg","floor":"#42","id":"1328468","time":"2018-3-17 23:05","userId":"295606","userName":"absurd","userSign":"(炸雞漢堡)","message":"你們都這麼高端嗎？我只是還是用筆記本（紙質版）<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"><img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"><img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"><br><br>那個onenote是怎麼用？<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"><img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"><img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/25/55/255501.jpg","floor":"#42-1","id":"1329191","time":"2018-3-19 20:07","userId":"kakinuma","userName":"事实是柿子 - ⭐️VIP3","userSign":"","message":"用手写设备当纸用"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/34/64/346405.jpg","floor":"#43","id":"1328785","time":"2018-3-18 15:50","userId":"346405","userName":"秋叶无歌","userSign":"(尽力做事。)","message":"默默看着。b38","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/36/31/363147.jpg","floor":"#44","id":"1328872","time":"2018-3-18 21:13","userId":"363147","userName":"败犬","userSign":"","message":"用CSDN的博客记录自己的读书笔记...虽然我并没有写多少这个","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/42/14268.jpg","floor":"#45","id":"1328903","time":"2018-3-18 22:44","userId":"calfn","userName":"触触✅个人认证","userSign":"","message":"都是大佬<br>用系统自带notes办公的就看看你们","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/25/55/255501.jpg","floor":"#46","id":"1328913","time":"2018-3-18 23:14","userId":"kakinuma","userName":"事实是柿子 - ⭐️VIP3","userSign":"(xD)","message":"为啥你们都是电子笔记啊<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"><br>能手写的电子设备一个个都好贵，而且看起来也没有想象中的方便","sub":[]}]